---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="description" content="leter.net abuse reporting and infrastructure transparency." />
    <title>Abuse & Transparency | leter.net</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="min-h-screen bg-surface">
      <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
        <a href="/" class="text-sm text-muted hover:text-text">‚Üê Back to home</a>
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-text">Abuse Reporting</h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Last updated: February 15, 2026</p>

        <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-muted">
          <p>
            leter.net operates under a strict anti-abuse policy to protect infrastructure trust and
            recipient safety.
          </p>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">1. Routing Transparency</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Email routing and processing for this domain are handled by a third-party
              infrastructure provider. leter.net does not operate public mailbox hosting or
              onboarding.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">2. Reporting Abuse</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              For abuse or security concerns related to this domain (including spam, phishing, or
              fraud), please contact: <span class="text-text">abuse@leter.net</span>.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Include full email headers and raw message source where possible to facilitate
              technical analysis.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">3. Administrative Action</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Aliases found to be in violation of anti-abuse policies or upstream provider terms
              will be removed immediately at the discretion of the domain administrator.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">4. Legal Escalation</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Legal correspondence: <span class="text-text">abuse@leter.net</span>
              <br />
              Copyright notices: use
              <a class="text-text underline decoration-accent/60 underline-offset-2" href="/dmca">
                DMCA process
              </a>
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
